name: NovaFrog Textual Inversion
description:
If you are here because you previously downloaded this and it's not working, either rename the file to "NovaFrogStyle.pt" or redownload it. I made an error and gave out the wrong keyword format... because I'm dumb.

I made this before my model. I feel like people will ask for it.

Trained on V1.5 examples use RealisticVisionV1.2

Dreambooth Model
